"(1) (i) The sky over the coastal horizon near Mumbai began to tremble with an unnatural rumble, a low, subterranean growl that rippled through the humid air. Zoe, standing on the windswept promenade, felt a sudden chill as the ground shuddered beneath her feet. Sulfuric stench clawed at her nostrils, mingling with the usual salt of the Arabian Sea. Above, dark plumes clawed their way into the atmosphere, blotting out the late afternoon sun and casting jagged shadows across the crowded streets.\n(2) (i) As the eruption intensified, a roaring column of ash and molten lava fragments erupted from a distant vent, unseen but unmistakable by its violent force. Zoe watched in awe and terror as the sky turned a bruised purple and the distant tremors turned to thunderous booms. The people nearby scattered in confusion, their faces etched with fear and disbelief, while Zoe’s breath quickened, her mind reeling with the raw, primal spectacle unfolding before her eyes in on . Greater Mumbai. June 14, 2025. Zoe Brown. witnessed a volcanic eruption."